Package org.jcvi.jillion.internal.trace.chromat.ztr

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ZtrChromatogramWriter
    ZtrChromatogramWriter writes out the given Chromatogram to the given OutputStream in ZTR format.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultZTRChromatogramWriterBuilder
    DefaultZTRChromatogramWriterBuilder is a Builder for ZtrChromatogramWriters that allows total control over what encoders are used in which order for every different field in a ZtrChromatogram.
    DefaultZTRChromatogramWriterBuilder.ChunkEncoderBuilder
    ChunkEncoderBuilder is a Builder which describes the order of the different encoding schemes used to encode each ZTR Chunk.
    ZTRChromatogramImpl  
    ZTRUtil
    Utility methods for manipulating ZTR data.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IOLibLikeZtrChromatogramWriter
    IOLibLikeZtrChromatogramWriter is a ZtrChromatogramWriter implementation that performs the same encoding operations in the same order as the staden IO_Lib C module.
